    kafedraIfo24: {
      first:
        'Students sent for study from Uzbekistan to Kyrgyzstan in 1990 were brought back. About 50 Uzbek students studying at the Bishkek Polytechnic Institute in the specialties "Technology of canned products", "Technology of meat and meat products", "Technology of milk and dairy products" were invited back to their country.',
      second:
        'Training in the specialty "Technology of canned products" at the Tashkent Chemical-Technological Institute was part of the Department of "Wine Technology" and lasted until 1994 and trained more than 100 specialists. In 1994, Doctor of Technical Sciences M.Vakil was hired by the leadership of the institute and was appointed head of the department in this specialty. After that, the department began to function independently.',
      third:
        'The department "Technology of meat and dairy products" was declared an independent department on August 24, 1991 after the creation of TCTI. In December 1991, at the Academic Council, a specialist in this field, associate professor U.Kuchkarov was appointed head of the department.',
      fourth:
        'In 1994, the rector of the institute, the head of the specialty "Technology of canned products" was appointed Doctor of Technical Sciences M.Vakil. Further, the department began to work independently. ',
      fivth:
        'In September 1999, the Department of Technology of Meat and Dairy Products was merged with the Department of Technology of Canned Products and renamed into the Department of “Technology of Meat, Milk, Fish and Canned Food”. In September 2005 the department was renamed into "Technology of canned food" and in February 2006 the head of the department was appointed dots. K.Dodaev.',
      sixth:
        'In September 2011, the Food Safety cycle was organized on the basis of the Department of "Technology of canned products". In 2012, the department was renamed into "Food Safety". The head of the department remained dots. K.Dodaev.',
      seventh:
        'Since September 2, 2014, the head of the department "Food Safety" was appointed  dos. A.Choriev.',
      eighth:
        'As a result of rotation in the structure of the institute, from September 2, 2020, it was renamed into the department "Technology of meat, dairy and canned products".The department employs highly qualified professors and teachers: Doctor of Technical Sciences, prof. K.Dodaev, Doctor of Technical Sciences, prof. M.Rakhimdzhanov, acting prof. U.Akhrorov, doc. A.Choriev, doc. D.Maksumova, PhD F.Eshmatov, doc. S.Atkhamova, doc. M.Zokirova, doc. O.Azizov; senior teachers: Sh.Tukhtaev, D.Zununova, A.Ibragimov, assistants U.Suyundukov, H.Niyozov, O.Samadov, R.Ernazarova, Z.Gafarova; technical staff K.Toirova and D.Vakhobova.',
      nineth:
        'From December 2, 2020, was appointed to the post of head of the department "Technology of meat, milk and canned products" PhD F.Eshmatov.',
      tenth:
        "The department employs highly qualified professors and teachers: Doctor of Technical Sciences, prof. K.Dodaev, Doctor of Technical Sciences, prof. M.Rakhimdzhanov, acting prof. U.Akhrorov, doc. A.Choriev, doc. D.Maksumova, PhD F.Eshmatov, doc. S.Atkhamova, doc. M.Zokirova, doc. O.Azizov; senior teachers: Sh.Tukhtaev, D.Zununova, A.Ibragimov, assistants U.Suyundukov, H.Niyozov, O.Samadov, R.Ernazarova, Z.Gafarova; technical staff K.Toirova and D.Vakhobova.",
      eleventh:
        'Nowadays, at the our department are studying in the bachelor`s degree in the direction of 5321000 - "Food technology (technology of meat and dairy products, food safety)", 5322700 - "Technology of canning" and 5322800 - "Technology of functional nutrition and infant products", in the master course in specialty 5A321001 - "Technology of production and processing of food products." products ("Technology of canned food, meat, dairy and fish products"), 5A321003 - Food safety and 5A610101 - "Sphere of services" (Masters in the specialty "Organization of production and services in catering" hours.',
      twelveth:
        "There is corporate cooperation with scientists of the Institute of Microbiology of the Academy of Sciences of the Republic of Uzbekistan, laboratories of the Institute of Chemistry of Plant Substances, Bioorganic Chemistry, Agro-Chemicals-Standard LLC, product certification bodies and laboratories and manufacturing enterprises to expand the educational and methodological base of the department.",
    },
    kafedraIfo24Third: {
      first:
        "Research work at the department is aimed at solving a number of problems in the food industry, including the development or improvement of technologies for the production of non-traditional products based on local raw materials, food additives, meat, dairy products and canned food. The safety of all food products is considered.",
      second:
        'For talented students, selected for scientific research and graduate students, the department has clubs "Sherbet", which means "Juice" and "Certificate-Service". They are attached to the professors and teachers of the department. That is, each student participating in this circle conducts research with his supervisor on the topic they have chosen. The results of his research will be published in collections of articles of scientific and technical conferences.',
      third:
        "The results of scientific research are applied in industrial enterprises and in the educational process.",
      fourth:
        "The department conducts research on the basis of different innovative projects. Constantly participates in fundamental, practical and innovative projects in the field of research of the teaching staff of the department.",
    },
