      a9: "Taking into account the training of the youth of the Republic of Karakalpakstan and the needs of the Kungrad soda plant for personnel with higher education, students from 2019-2020 academic year were accepted to bakalavriatura in 4 directions for correspondence education for the training of young people without separation from production in the form of 4+1 correspondence education.",
